---
title: Sweet & Smoky Sirloin with Roasted Broccoli, Mashed Potatoes & Cherry Sauce
description: If you’re craving something that’s good and hearty, this recipe has got you covered. Pork tenderloin is rubbed with cinnamon and smoked paprika, which brings a layer of warm aromatics to the meat. It’s then roasted and drizzled in a cherry jam sauce that adds sweetness to all that savory. Roasted broccoli on the side adds a fresh pop of green, while mashed potatoes keep things creamy and classic.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/627bdaa6bf9d55be3a0db8f2-311bcc2b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/sweet-smoky-sirloin-627bdaa6bf9d55be3a0db8f2-111d4ff5.pdf
